4:
You're back. I was surprised to
suddenly get a letter from you.
7: Father, I'm sorry! I broke our promise.
9:
I ended up protecting a yokai the
other day! But he in turn protected a
human child...
10:
Which didn't go too well, so we
ended up taking charge of that
child.
13:
What is it you want to say? Your face
tells me you didn't return simply to
apologize.
17:
That yokai protected the child just
like you always used to protect me,
Father!
18:
So I've come to a decision. Doesn't
matter if they're human or yokai—
25:
I'm going to wield my sword for the
sake of the weak and oppressed!
28:
So that is the answer you've found
for yourself...
29:
It will undoubtedly be a most
treacherous path. Knowing that, do
you still wish to go through with this?
43:
Not once have I ever thought to aid
the yokai... Perhaps the times have
changed.
49:
You've got nowhere else to run!
You're done for!
52:
Careful. A beast backed into a
corner is not to be underestimated.
56: Yep, yep, I know! Here goes—
59: Ooh, look at them go. You ready?
64:
Back off, kids! You shouldn't even be
here! If that monster targets you—
68: Tsk, no point talking it out!
73:
*sigh* Didn't I tell you kids earlier not
to come this way?!
82:
Well, they're okay now thanks to you,
Kuramaru.
86:
You're too soft, Alk. They might be
yokai, but children still need to be
taught to do the right thing!
89: You're a child too! Child, child!
93:
Gah! When someone is angry at
you, you need to listen to them,
okay?!
97:
Kuramaru's really warmed up to
yokai, huh.
101:
He gets along well enough with our
yokai friends too.
106:
Hard to believe this is coming from
the guy who was shouting about
cutting down all yokai before, heh.
110: H-hey, relax! I know better now!
117:
I still have a bad habit of wanting to
draw my sword the moment I see a
yokai though!
122:
That's definitely one scary habit you
want to break!
127:
I guess we'll want to keep our
distance from Kuramaru until he
does.
131:
I'm getting shivers just recalling that
time Kuramaru swing his blade at
me...
136:
Oh, right... That's when we first met
at the village.
142:
Sorry about that! Won't happen
again!
146:
Speaking of that village, they found
foster parents for the child we took
from the yokai's charge.
154:
Yes, I went to take a look earlier. He
seemed happy.
158:
Thank goodness... I guess the yokai's
efforts weren't in vain after all.
160:
I hope those two get to see each
other again someday.
162:
I doubt that'll happen anytime soon,
but at least they're both alive and
well.
166: I'm sure it'll be possible one day.
171:
All right, you guys ready to get on
with the next assignment? Some
yokai have been causing trouble
near the village.
175: So you're on the side of humans?
178:
That might've been the case before,
but not anymore!
182:
Be they human or yokai, I consider
myself an ally of anyone who needs
my help!
183:
So if you're ever in trouble, just call
out for me! No matter where I might
be, I'll rush to your aid!
